Introduction

P1Harmony is a six-member boy group under FNC Entertainment. They debuted on October 28, 2020, with their first mini-album Disharmony : Stand Out. Prior to their debut, they released a short film titled "P1H: The Beginning of a New World".

They have a series on their YouTube channel called 'P1ustyle H' in which they do covers, both dancing and singing. They did their first US Tour this year, called '2022 P1Harmony Live Tour - P1ustage H: PEACE'.

On April 7, it was announced that P1Harmony will release their first Japanese best album Love & P1ece : The Best of P1Harmony in August.
